james p langa named senior vice president of hardinge inc nasdaqhdng             share this on delicious digg facebook linkedin twitter what is this « previous release  next release » may   james p langa named senior vice president of hardinge inc elmira ny may   – hardinge inc nasdaq hdng a leading international provider of advanced metalcutting solutions today announced that james p langa  has been promoted to the position of senior vice president – asian operations  he will report to mr richard l simons president and chief executive officer  “jim has been involved in the engineering and supply chain activities of our asian operations for the past three years and has made significant contributions to the company’s growth in this region” said mr simons “we are pleased to have a person of jim’s ability leading the expansion of our engineering manufacturing and sales efforts in this region”     mr langa joined hardinge in  as vice presidentgeneral manager north american machine operations  since  he has been vice president global engineering quality and strategic sourcing prior to joining hardinge mr langa spent  years in a variety of management positions with the wellman products group a division of hawk corporation including responsibilities in china hardinge is a global designer manufacturer and distributor of machine tools specializing in super precision™ and precision cnc lathes high performance machining centers highend cylindrical and jig grinding machines and technologically advanced workholding  rotary products the company’s products are distributed to most of the industrialized markets around the world with approximately  of the  sales outside of north america hardinge has a very diverse international customer base and serves a wide variety of enduser markets this customer base includes metalworking manufacturers which make parts for a variety of industries as well as a wide range of end users in the aerospace agricultural transportation basic consumer goods communications and electronics construction defense energy pharmaceutical and medical equipment and recreation industries among others the company has manufacturing operations in switzerland taiwan the united states china and the united kingdom hardinge’s common stock trades on the nasdaq global select market under the symbol “hdng” for more information please visit httpwwwhardingecom close window  back to top delicious digg facebook linkedin twitter copyright  hardinge inc   zoominfo page not found james p langa  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in james p langa senior vice president machine solutions at hardinge inc view full profile are you james p langa claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view james p langas full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in james p langas network and community follow changes in james p langas employment and moneyinmotion connect with james p langa through your network of contacts james p langas executive work history current senior vice president machine solutions hardinge inc past to view james p langas complete executive work history sign up now age      james p langas biography enior vice president  machine solutions since february  senior vice presidentasia operations may   february  vice presidentglobal engineering quality and strategic sourcing september   april  vice presidentgeneral managernorth american operations january   september  vice presidentgeneral manager north american machine operations june   january  director original equipment sales  marketing for wellman products group division of hawk corporation  and focus factory manager for wellman products group  source hardinge inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view james p langas full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like james p langa more specifically youll be able to ident